  "source": "[A \\:subset:/ B]\nDescribes: A\nwhen: B is \\set\nextends: A is \\set\nsatisfies:\n. forAll: x \"in\" A\n  then: x \"in\" B\nDocumented:\n. called: \"subset\"\n. written: \"A? \\subseteq B?\"\n. description: \"$A$ is a subset of $B$, written $A \\subseteq B$, when every element of $A$ is also an element of $B$.\"\nId: \"4196f823-e51d-4568-89aa-83a2d4627bd9\"",
